Barython [WORK IN PROGRESS]
===========================

Configures Lemonboys's bar and brings some widgets in trying to stay
performance friendly. Handles multiple screen and is focused to be BSPWM
compatible.

The project is not functionnal yet.

Installation
------------

Just run:

```
pip3 -e . install
```


